{"tid":1004173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"身邊朋友突然開始蝗化","createTime":"2019-02-01T08:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T11:20:46.000Z","uid":172709,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2ee02c084f5ae0681537cdde65bca6ba17f05645","tid":1004173,"uid":172709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T08:48:34.000Z","msg":"近排見返個老友，以前佢係一個幾反共嘅人黎，佢唔鍾意政府，對好多人同事不滿，會去參與遊行集會等等。點知近來見佢，突然聽佢用多好多蝗語，雖然佢個格同無咩變到好似大陸人咁衰，但聽佢講野真係好奇怪，傾計會話人好牛，會用咩&ldquo;三不沾&ldquo;黎形容籃球嘅airball。問佢做咩變成咁，佢話而家香港無前途，遲早都會被大陸同化，無錢離開唯有盡早適應，要學好普通話，先會講野有咁嘅習慣。聽到我好灰，但睇黎都係唯一方法。。。"},{"pid":"0019832c5faeb3b10255afb43230039e2f80d5dc","tid":1004173,"uid":172709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T08:51:26.000Z","msg":"有無人都咁"},{"pid":"f6a56c560670d1e7d7b6982d7bc758b23416c7c6","tid":1004173,"uid":64374,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T08:53:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bc194eeff314001eabde66bc9f84e25f7241d35","tid":1004173,"uid":136221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:16:16.000Z","msg":"你唔好跟住佢咁on9"},{"pid":"08adeabcc93bd9a2555099b0f5c30d1751e6c942","tid":1004173,"uid":38426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:19:52.000Z","msg":"skr skr<br />\n屌奶聲有個舊同學都係咁 成撚日返深圳<br />\n死港女"},{"pid":"5587ce11834e0a0f4c201519501b06698a243aa2","tid":1004173,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:39:36.000Z","msg":"喜茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04421d93819cde9d145bde8bc32e6488c52f63d3","tid":1004173,"uid":172709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bc194eeff314001eabde66bc9f84e25f7241d35","tid":1004173,"uid":136221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:16:16.000Z","msg":"你唔好跟住佢咁on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi